    <span class="like-count"></span>
  </span>
<span class="squarespace-social-buttons inline-style" data-system-data-id="" data-asset-url="https://static1.squarespace.com/static/56d4a27bb654f96f882909e4/5e8389a191b02a016840e33e/64e4fdb3d4a39b0f953772a3/1692729142616/" data-record-type="1" data-full-url="/blog/2023/8/22/laws-taking-effect-july-1" data-title="Laws Taking Effect July 1"></span>
